20:03.780 --> 20:05.070
(Chattering)

20:16.080 --> 20:18.090
Where to?

20:25.890 --> 20:27.890
Sir, where do you want to go?

20:31.020 --> 20:34.480
Anywhere. First bus.

20:39.320 --> 20:40.650
Buffalo?

20:43.400 --> 20:45.320
One way.

20:47.700 --> 20:50.330
That'll be a dollar twenty.

22:32.760 --> 22:35.770
[Man Speaking Indistinctly Over PA]

23:03.460 --> 23:04.960
I want to rent a car.

23:05.130 --> 23:07.630
Would you fill this out, please?

23:22.980 --> 23:25.980
