03:36:10.700 --> 03:36:15.410
Many years ago I had a friend,
a dear friend.

03:36:17.040 --> 03:36:20.290
I turned him in to save his life...

03:36:20.500 --> 03:36:22.800
...but he was killed.

03:36:24.090 --> 03:36:26.930
But he wanted it that way.

03:36:27.970 --> 03:36:30.180
It was a great friendship.

03:36:33.270 --> 03:36:37.310
It went bad for him
and it went bad for me too.

03:36:42.280 --> 03:36:44.440
Good night, Mr. Bailey.

03:36:53.620 --> 03:36:57.330
I hope the investigation
turns out to be nothing.

03:36:59.250 --> 03:37:03.300
It'd be a shame to see
a lifetime of work go to waste.

